<br>
What is the general consensus of the server? Meaning what Velious Faction are you or your guild on?  My regular hunting partner and I are trying to decide what faction to be on and we both would like to be on Dragon Faction. We think it would be different and fun from our other characters who have spent their lives on Coldain faction. <br>
<br>
It would also be helpful to know which guilds are on what as well because at some point, I would like to join a guild that not only stands for the things that we stand for (i.e. EVIL) but also is on the same Velious faction.  <p><p align="center"><img src="http://www.antique-index.com/photostore/totf/barritt.jpg"><br><a href="http://www.geocities.com/barrittahl" target="_blank">Barritt's Adventures</a><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/urhavingaidin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhavin Gaidin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/24/02 10:34:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2190.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction question</span><hr size=1> Well.. for one, if you go Pro Dragon, you dont have to destroy Coldain, and its really even for the server, as it is on most. there isint really a wrong way to go..<br>
But id stick to keeping the coldain happy, because there are only a few guilds on this server who can get the dragon/giant armor drops... i think ^_^ <p>
